{"tid":1643180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 唔係六大呀","createTime":"2019-10-10T04:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:46:41.000Z","uid":138407,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d6ec56a259fdaa61a992f8be085e19f2e31c8e","tid":1643180,"uid":138407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"我地上街咁耐都係叫緊五大訴求<br />\n唔至係香港人共識，都係外媒對我地堅定信念嘅印象<br />\n如果你想加就加 六大就六大 你係大台？<br />\n外人要不割 不斷比你騎劫<br />\n人地外媒只會覺得我地貪得無厭<br />\n五大都未得仲六大？<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 反抗</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c2b6b17c79a4d8fc8e945e72f4144004801251","tid":1643180,"uid":138407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c12139d20176b29c8f1ded8715b605fbf8c47c6e","tid":1643180,"uid":184144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3a2e81255837ad5a74afa233a206f0ec7ffb700","tid":1643180,"uid":14052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:21:12.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"b667c1d4a7df280b2b5480fc90a26db04de2df5a","tid":1643180,"uid":75778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"六佢老母 on99"},{"pid":"7f0f28dcf180aea7fb677c5006bbd79503b8bd61","tid":1643180,"uid":267277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"agree <br />\n5大達成左，第6根本無難度<br />\n反而5大變6大，真係會令人覺得貪得無厭"},{"pid":"9fab1c268ccad994ba58db357f93dd46794eddf8","tid":1643180,